opment of this sensing\ntechnology could also potentially be applied to other soft compliant grippers,\nincreasing their viability in many different fields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Apr 2022 17:56:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-15"}
