er all $n$ vertices by copies of any given graph $H$ in $d_{\\min}(H) n +\no(n)$ rounds whp, where $d_{\\min}(H)$ is the minimum degree of a vertex in $H$,\nwhich is a factor of 2 away from a corresponding deterministic lower bound.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Apr 2022 08:26:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-18"}
