 role that dynamical phase transitions could play\nin self-organized intracellular responses of plant cells towards environmental\ncues.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Apr 2022 08:50:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 28 Sep 2022 12:03:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-22"}
